title: Murray, Carroll lead Eagles to 27-7 win over Giants (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,385 Murray, Carroll lead Eagles to 27-7 win over Giants (Yahoo Sports) PHILADELPHIA (AP) -- DeMarco Murray ran for 109 yards and a touchdown, Nolan Carroll returned one of Eli Manning's two interceptions for a score and the Philadelphia Eagles beat the New York Giants 27-7 Monday night.
